data.description: Welcome home! A gorgeous 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home in the water privileged community of Woodland Beach! Enjoy an updated spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Have fun with family and friends on your large private deck in your fenced backyard. Large master bedroom with 2 spacious spare rooms. The community offers beaches with netted swimming areas, boat slips, boat ramp, kayak launch, picnic area and playground. The home’s vinyl siding is practically new as it was replaced within the last 2 years enhancing the home's curb appeal. Both bathrooms were recently updated within the last 2 years as well. Easy commute to DC, Baltimore, Annapolis, Joint Base Andrews, and Fort Meade.
